==Awards and nominations==
[[John Simm]] won a Royal Television Society North West Award for "Best Male Performance" in the first series of ''Prey''. The series was also nominated for a 2015 BAFTA Television Award in the category "Mini Series".<ref>{{cite web|last=Wightman |first=Catriona |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a640375/bafta-television-awards-2015-this-years-nominees-in-full.html |title=BAFTA Television Awards 2015: This year's nominees in full |website=Digitalspy.co.uk |date=2015-04-08 |accessdate=2016-04-01}}</ref>

